== 與人類關係 ==
君主斑蝶是[[阿拉巴馬州|阿拉巴馬州]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.archives.state.al.us/emblems/st_insec.html |title=Official Alabama Insect |accessdate=2007-03-19 |date=2001-07-12 |work=Alabama Emblems, Symbols and Honors |publisher=Alabama Department of Archives & History |archive-date=2018-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181014061225/http://www.archives.state.al.us/emblems/st_insec.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[愛達荷州|愛達荷州]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.shgresources.com/id/symbols/insect/ |title=Idaho Symbols, Insect: Monarch Butterfly |accessdate=2008-03-26 |work=Idaho State Symbols, Emblems, and Mascots |publisher=SHG resources, state handbook & guide |archive-date=2012-07-10 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/693lxetwe?url=http://www.shgresources.com/id/symbols/insect/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[伊利諾州|伊利諾州]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.museum.state.il.us/exhibits/symbols/insect.html |title=State Symbol: Illinois Official Insect — Monarch Butterfly (''Danaus plexippus'') |accessdate=2008-03-26 |work=[Illinois] State Symbols |publisher=Illinois State Museum |archive-date=2018-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224225140/http://www.illinoisstatemuseum.org/content/online-resources |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[明尼蘇達州|明尼蘇達州]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.house.leg.state.mn.us/hinfo/govser/GOVSER2.pdf |format=PDF |accessdate=2008-03-26 |title=Minnesota State Symbols |publisher=Minnesota House of Representatives |archive-date=2018-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224225136/http://www.house.leg.state.mn.us/hinfo/govser/GOVSER2.pdf%20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>及[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tsl.state.tx.us/ref/abouttx/symbols.html |accessdate=2008-03-26 |title=Texas State Symbols |publisher=The Texas State Library and Archives |archive-date=2018-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224225130/https://www.tsl.texas.gov/ref/abouttx/symbols.html%20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>的州昆蟲，且是[[佛蒙特州|佛蒙特州]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.libraries.vermont.gov/www/html/emblems/butterfly.htm |accessdate=2008-03-26 |title=(Vermont) State Butterfly |publisher=Vermont Department of Libraries |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080518004053/http://www.libraries.vermont.gov/www/html/emblems/butterfly.htm |archivedate=2008-05-18 }}</ref>及[[西維珍尼亞州|西維珍尼亞州]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wv.gov/govdirectory/statgeninfo.pdf |accessdate=2008-03-26 |format=PDF |title=West Virginia Statistical Information, General State Information |publisher=Official West Virginia Web Portal |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080411045927/http://www.wv.gov/govdirectory/statgeninfo.pdf |archivedate=2008-04-11 }}</ref>的州蝴蝶。於1990年，君主斑蝶與[[西方蜜蜂|西方蜜蜂]]一同被提名為[[美國|美國]]的國昆蟲<ref>{{cite news |first=Nicholas |last=Wade |title=Choosing a National Bug |publisher=The New York Times |date=1990-06-01 |accessdate=2008-03-26 |url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9C0CE4D81439F932A35755C0A966958260 |archive-date=2009-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090210073628/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9C0CE4D81439F932A35755C0A966958260 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但最終卻不獲通過<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.entsoc.org/resources/faq.htm#triv7 |accessdate=2008-03-26 |title=Frequently Asked Questions on Entomology |publisher=Entomological Society of America |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080331054437/http://www.entsoc.org/resources/faq.htm#triv7 |archivedate=2008-03-31 }}</ref>。

很多人很種植蝴蝶園來吸引[[蝴蝶|蝴蝶]]。其他的則會為了喜好及教育來飼養君主斑蝶。在一些君主斑蝶遷徙的位點會建立庇護區<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.sciencedaily.com/videos/2005/0810-saving_butterflies.htm |title= Saving Butterflies Insect Ecologist Spearheads Creation of Oases for Endangered Butterflies |accessdate= 2008-05-27 |publisher= ScienceDaily |date= 2005-01-01 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20080604045408/http://www.sciencedaily.com/videos/2005/0810-saving_butterflies.htm |archivedate= 2008-06-04 }}</ref>，而旅遊業亦因此應運而生。

很多學校都會由[[毛蟲|毛蟲]]開始養殖君主斑蝶。當成蟲後就會被放生野外<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.monarchwatch.org/ |title= Monarch Watch |accessdate= 2008-05-27 |publisher= The Kansas Biological Survey, Univ of Kansas |date= 2008-05-27 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20071112042846/http://www.monarchwatch.org/ |archive-date= 2007-11-12 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>。

== 威脅 ==
君主斑蝶過冬的地方被非法砍伐導致牠們的數量大幅下降。現時正努力將牠們列為受保護動物及恢復其棲息地。[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]估計於2005年至2006年間，君主斑蝶的數量會有明顯增長。

=== 掠食者 ===
雖然君主斑蝶是吃[[乳草|乳草]]的，但是不同種類、不同植物或不同部位的乳草有不同的[[卡烯內酯|卡烯內酯]]含量，這亦反映在君主斑蝶體內[[毒素|毒素]]的含量。所以君主斑蝶未必一定是不可吃的，而是进行了[[自擬態|自擬態]]。一些君主斑蝶的[[掠食者|掠食者]]懂得量度牠們的毒素，並吐出高卡烯內酯含量的昆蟲。

卡烯內酯是積聚在君主斑蝶的[[腹部|腹部]]及翅膀。一些掠食者亦會將這些部位撕開，去吃其他的部份<ref name= Barbosa>{{cite book en |last=Barbosa |first=Pedro |coauthors= Deborah Kay Letourneau |title=Novel Aspects of Insect-plant Interactions |url= http://books.google.fr/books?id=2fZbhllItE4C&pg=PA45&dq=monarch+predators+asclepias&sig=bnjfIdmBqSFoBcB9L6FPAVoeTTA#PPA31,M1 |accessdate=2008-05-12 |year=1988 |publisher=Wiley-Interscience |isbn= 0471832766 |pages=29-31 |chapter=5 }}</ref>。[[鳥類|鳥類]]掠食者包括[[褐噪鶇|褐噪鶇]]、[[白頭翁|白頭翁]]、[[美洲鶇|美洲鶇]]、[[美洲雀科|美洲雀科]]、[[麻雀|麻雀]]、[[叢鴉屬|叢鴉屬]]及[[藍頭松鴉|藍頭松鴉]]。<ref name= Barbosa/>在[[北美洲|北美洲]]，[[異色瓢蟲|異色瓢蟲]]的幼蟲或成蟲會吃君主斑蝶的卵或初出生的幼蟲<ref>{{cite journal en |last=Koch |first=R. L. |coauthors=W. D. Hutchison, R. C. Venette and G. E. Heimpel |title=Susceptibility of immature monarch butterfly, ''Danaus plexippus'' (Lepidoptera: Nymphalidae: Danainae), to predation by ''Harmonia axyridis'' (Coleoptera: Coccinellidae) |journal=Biological Control |volume=28 |issue=2 |pages=265–270 |doi=10.1016/S1049-9644(03)00102-6 |url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=ArticleURL&_udi=B6WBP-48TKDRR-6&_user=1072191&_rdoc=1&_fmt=&_orig=search&_sort=d&view=c&_acct=C000051289&_version=1&_urlVersion=0&_userid=1072191&md5=fb8ace3d840cb24a87d5d7276ef7bb6c |accessdate=2008-04-23 |date=October 2003 |archive-date=2009-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090918122829/http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=ArticleURL&_udi=B6WBP-48TKDRR-6&_user=1072191&_rdoc=1&_fmt=&_orig=search&_sort=d&view=c&_acct=C000051289&_version=1&_urlVersion=0&_userid=1072191&md5=fb8ace3d840cb24a87d5d7276ef7bb6c |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[File:albino_monarch_butterfly.jpg|right]]的白色形態的君主斑蝶。]]
在[[歐胡島|歐胡島]]，有一種白色形態的君主斑蝶。這是由於在1965年及1966年引入了[[黑喉紅臀鵯|黑喉紅臀鵯]]及''Pycnonotus jacosus''。牠們是最普遍的吃[[昆蟲|昆蟲]]鳥類，也可能是唯一會吃君主斑蝶的鳥類。在[[夏威夷|夏威夷]]的君主斑蝶只有低含量的卡烯內酯，而這些鳥類亦可以忍受這種毒素。這兩種鳥會吃君主斑蝶的幼蟲及[[蛹|蛹]]，也會吃正在休息的成蟲，但很少吃飛行中的成蟲。所以白色君主斑蝶比橙色的有較高的生存率。這可能是因[[異類選擇|異類選擇]]或[[偽裝|偽裝]]<ref>{{cite journal en |last=Stimson |first=John |coauthors=Mark Berman |year=1990 |title=Predator induced colour polymorphism in ''Danaus plexippus'' L. (Lepidoptera: Nymphalidae) in Hawaii |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_heredity_1990-12_65_3/page/401 |journal=Heredity |volume=65 |issue=3 |pages=401–406 |accessdate=2008-04-06 |laysummary=http://md1.csa.com/partners/viewrecord.php?requester=gs&collection=ENV&recid=2472199&q=predator+induced+colour+polymorphism&uid=792450984&setcookie=yes |doi=10.1038/hdy.1990.110 |archive-date=2012-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120223143620/http://md1.csa.com/partners/viewrecord.php?requester=gs&collection=ENV&recid=2472199&q=predator+induced+colour+polymorphism&uid=792450984&setcookie=yes |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

=== 寄生蟲 ===
君主斑蝶的[[寄生蟲|寄生蟲]]是[[寄生蠅|寄生蠅]]''Lesperia archippivora''。被寄生的幼蟲會繼續脫毛及懸掛自己，但卻於成[[蛹|蛹]]前死亡。此時一種白色的[[蛆|蛆]]會從幼蟲中出來及被絲線懸掛。蛆會在地上形成褐色的蛹<ref name=Brewer>{{cite journal en |last=Brewer |first=Jo |coauthors=Gerard M. Thomas |year=1966 |title=Causes of death encountered during rearing of ''Danaus plexippus'' (Danaidae) |journal=Journal of The Lepidopterist’s Society |volume=20 |issue=4 |pages=235–238 |url=http://research.yale.edu/peabody/jls/pdfs/1960s/1966/1966-20(4)235-Brewer.pdf |format=PDF |accessdate=2008-04-13 |laysummary=http://research.yale.edu/peabody/jls/htms/1960s/1966-20(4)235-Brewer.htm |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090325051238/http://research.yale.edu/peabody/jls/pdfs/1960s/1966/1966-20%284%29235-Brewer.pdf |archivedate=2009-03-25 }}</ref>。

一種[[微球菌屬|微球菌屬]]的''Micrococcus flacidifex danai''亦會影響幼蟲及導致死亡。君主斑蝶幼蟲在成蛹前會如常的走到水平面上，但於幾小時後死亡，屍體仍然以後腹腳懸掛。該屍體會在很短時間變為黑色。另外，[[綠膿桿菌|綠膿桿菌]]雖沒有入侵能力，但卻會引發繼發感染。這些都是在實驗室飼養的君主斑蝶死亡的原因<ref name = Brewer/>。

一種稱為''Ophryocystis elektroscirrha''的[[原生動物|原生動物]]是君主斑蝶的另一種寄生蟲。牠會感染皮下組織，並以在蛹時期長成的[[孢子|孢子]]傳播。孢子會在受感染的整隻君主斑蝶身體，而大部份集中在腹部。這些孢子會在雌蝶產卵時被擦掉，而出生後的毛蟲則會吃下並受感柒染。嚴重感染的身體會變得虛弱，不能展開翅膀及壽命較短。經過幾代後仍會有感染的情況<ref>{{cite journal en |last=Leong |first= K. L. H. |coauthors=M. A. Yoshimura, H. K. Kaya and H. Williams |year=1997 |title= Instar Susceptibility of the Monarch Butterfly (''Danaus plexippus'') to the Neogregarine Parasite, ''Ophryocystis elektroscirrha'' |journal=Journal of Invertebrate Pathology |volume=69 |issue=1 |pages=79–83  |accessdate=2008-04-15 |doi=10.1006/jipa.1996.4634 |laysummary=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=ArticleURL&_udi=B6WJV-45S96SB-D&_user=10&_rdoc=1&_fmt=&_orig=search&_sort=d&view=c&_acct=C000050221&_version=1&_urlVersion=0&_userid=10&md5=7d4874a42d109805f3a1e77129046e4f }}</ref>。

